  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Effect of rTMS on Attention in Adults Diagnosed With Attention-Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Effect of rTMS on Attention in Adults Diagnosed With ADHD</official_title>
